---
layout : base.njk
title : MAC Fit 2 - North
coach:
    name: Jen Bronson
    email: jbronson@swimmaccarolina.org
---

{% banner title, {image: 'teen-fit.jpg'} %}

<main id="main" class="bg-gray-100 py-6">
    <div class="container overflow-hidden">
        <p>
            <a href="/">Home</a> /
            <a href="/mac-fit/">MAC Fit</a> /
            <a href="/mac-fit/mac-fit-north">Mac Fit North</a> /
            {{ title }}
        </p>

        <h2>MAC Fit 2 (formerly Teen Fit)</h2>

        <p class="lead">
            Love the water but not ready for year-round competitive swimming?
            MAC Fit is perfect for swimmers who want to stay in shape, build endurance, improve technique, and prepare for school or summer league team tryouts.
            Each session combines aerobic conditioning, stroke refinement, and skill-building drills in a fun, positive environment, helping swimmers gain confidence, stay active, and enjoy the sportâ€”without the pressure of competition.
        </p>

        <div class="card p-4">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4">
                    <p>14 - 17 year old swimmers who can swim</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>50 yards freestyle with bilateral side breathing</li>
                        <li>50 yards backstroke with straight leg kicking &amp; body rotation</li>
                        <li>50 yards breaststroke with legal breaststroke kick (feet flexed &amp; toes turned out)</li>
                        <li>50 yards butterfly with dolphin kick, knowledge of stroke concept to build on</li>
                        <li>Swimmers must be comfortable diving into the pool</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4">
                    <h2>Structure</h2>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Evaluations are held intermittently throughout the year <br>
                            <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeeXP5tx0rLbDc97S4Gpk7c1Tpe9kkUq_RLcfjny7taKE-7iQ/viewform" class="button" target="_blank">Sign up for an evaluation </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>Swimmers can sign up for multiple classes depending on their goals</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="mt-8">Pricing</h2>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Annual (September-August) Registration Fees (includes swim cap and t-shirt)
                            <ul class="list-none">
                                <li>$32 for first swimmer</li>
                                <li>$26 for second swimmer</li>
                                <li>$22 for third swimmer</li>
                                <li>Free for fourth+ swimmer</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Tuition Price
                            <ul class="list-none">
                                <li>$25.00 per 45 min class</li>
                                <li>$33.00 per 60 min class</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            <div class="text-right">
                <a href="https://app3.jackrabbitclass.com/portal/ppLogin.asp?id=541680" class="button button--small mb-3" target="_blank">
                    Portal Login
                </a>
            </div>

            <h3 class="separator-center">Bridge Program Clinics Calendar</h3>
            <div class="my-8 mx-auto" style="max-width: 800px;">
                <iframe src="https://app3.jackrabbitclass.com/eventcalendar.asp?orgid=541680" width="100%" height="650" scrolling="yes" class="iframe-class" frameborder="0"></iframe>
            </div>

            <h3 class="separator-center">Schedule and Registration for MAC Fit North</h3>

            {% if jackrabbit.MACFitNorth.sessions.length > 0 %}
                {% for session in jackrabbit.MACFitNorth.sessions %}
                <h3 class="separator-left mt-12">{{ session.session }}</h3>

                <script src="https://app.jackrabbitclass.com/jr3.0/Openings/OpeningsJS?OrgID={{ jackrabbit.MACFitNorth.orgId }}&amp;Session={{ session.session }}&amp;cat2=MAC%20Fit%202&amp;showCols=location,Cat1,Cat2&amp;hidecols=Class,Gender,Session,ages&amp;style=font-size:16px&amp;sort=days" type="text/javascript"></script>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <div class="bg-red-100 border border-red-900 p-4 my-6">
                    There are no scheduled MAC Fit classes at this time
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            {% coachContact coach.name, coach.email, coach.phone %}
        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            {% include 'hffa-map.njk' %}
        </div>
    </div>

</main>